module.name: org.opencms.editors.fckeditor
module.description:
This module adds the popular Open Source HTML editor "FCKeditor" to the OpenCms Workplace.

Install this module if you want a WYSIWYG editor for Mozilla based browsers, Internet Explorer, Safari or Google Chrome. The version of FCKeditor is 2.6.3
